_sName: aim_nostril - a map for you who like nostrils
_sText:
So it's basically one of these aim, 1v1 thing maps. it holds 3 slots per team, and that's basically it. it's pretty good though.
When you fall in the water you have 5-7 seconds or so to get to the door and out, or else you will be stuck in there, and most likely get killed by the enemy team.

That's like the only semi-special thing about this map, I was gonna put it on the workshop until i realised css doesn't have an official workshop.. So I thought of gamebanana and, here the map is.
Back to the map, it's your basic 3v3, 1v1, arena, aim, sort of map. Have fun!
